(3, '1', '182171-28-01-2023-1674874525.jpg', 'Four Points by Sheraton Bur Dubai', NULL, '<p>This 4-star hotel in Bur Dubai city centre features elegant rooms and is 7 minutes from Bur Juman Shopping Mall by foot. It offers free parking.</p>\n\n<p>The modern rooms at the Four Points by Sheraton Bur Dubai have a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, tea and coffee-making facilities.</p>\n\n<p>A delicious and lavish breakfast buffet is served every morning. Guests can also enjoy fine dining at the hotel&rsquo;s award-winning Indian Restaurant, which is decorated with beautiful Indian art.</p>\n\n<p>State-of-the-art facilities include a gym equipped with cardiovascular equipment and an outdoor swimming pool surrounded by sun loungers.</p>\n\n<p>Four Points is a 10-minute drive from the Dubai International Airport, the Dubai World Trade Center and Jumeirah Beach Park.</p>\n\n<p>Business travellers particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it <strong>8.2</strong> for a work-related trip.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Four Points by Sheraton Bur Dubai has been welcoming Booking.com guests since 8 Jun 2007.</strong><br />\nHotel chain/brand: Four Points by Sheraton</p>', '4', 0, '1', '20230311051701100', 'Dubai', '25.2576215,55.2994854', NULL, NULL, '[\"16\"]', '<p>For security purposes, it is mandatory to show a valid passport or state-issued photo ID at check-in. This hotel can arrange a visa for you after your reservation is made. Please contact them via phone or email (details provided in your confirmation). Please present the credit card used to make this reservation upon check-in at the hotel. If you are booking on behalf of someone else, you must contact the hotel directly to arrange for third party billing. Please note that there is an additional 15 AED tourism fee per bedroom per unit per night payable at the hotel directly Please note that Antique bazaar will be closed for lunch and dinner from 4 - 7 June, 2022. Operations will resume from 8 June, 2022 onwards.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 'USD', 'Khalid Bin Al Waleed Rd - Bur Dubai - Al Hamriya - Dubai - United Arab Emirates', '02:00:00', '02:00:00', '<p>For security purposes, it is mandatory to show a valid passport or state-issued photo ID at check-in. This hotel can arrange a visa for you after your reservation is made. Please contact them via phone or email (details provided in your confirmation). Please present the credit card used to make this reservation upon check-in at the hotel. If you are booking on behalf of someone else, you must contact the hotel directly to arrange for third party billing. Please note that there is an additional 15 AED tourism fee per bedroom per unit per night payable at the hotel directly Please note that Antique bazaar will be closed for lunch and dinner from 4 - 7 June, 2022. Operations will resume from 8 June, 2022 onwards.</p>', 18),
(4, '1', '699345-28-01-2023-1674874904.jpg', 'Voco Dubai an IHG Hotel', NULL, '<p>With a premium location on Sheikh Zayed Road, this 5-star hotel overlooks the Dubai World Trade Centre. It features 4 restaurants, an outdoor pool and spacious meeting rooms.</p>\n\n<p>471 guestrooms and suites share a contemporary style characterized by marbled entrances and vivid accent colours. Every room also showcases free high-speed wireless Internet, a flat-screen LCD television, an alarm clock and has a spacious bathroom with luxury amenities.</p>\n\n<p>voco Dubai (Formerly Nassima Royal Hotel) features international restaurants, offering a variety of world cuisines, while the bars provide places to unwind after a day in the city.</p>\n\n<p>Guests can enjoy state-of-the-art recreation facilities, including an outdoor pool area with a view of Jumeirah Beach, a health club, with options of personal training, as well as the luxury Spa Zen.</p>\n\n<p>voco Dubai (Formerly Nassima Royal Hotel) offers airport pick up adnd drop off.</p>\n\n<p>The Dubai Mall, The Museum of the Future and Jumeirah Beach are in close proximity and 5 minutes&rsquo; drive away only. Dubai International Airport is 15 minutes drive away from the hotel as well.</p>\n\n<p>Business travellers particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it <strong>9.0</strong> for a work-related trip.</p>\n\n<p><strong>voco Dubai, an IHG Hotel has been welcoming Booking.com guests since 14 Nov 2010.</strong><br />\nHotel chain/brand: Voco</p>', '5', 0, '1', '20230311051701100', 'Dubai', '25.2048493,55.2707828', NULL, NULL, '[\"14\",\"18\",\"20\",\"23\"]', '<p>In accordance with government guidelines to minimise transmission of the Coronavirus (COVID-19), this property may request additional documentation from guests to validate identity, travel itinerary and other relevant information, during dates where such guidelines exist. In response to Coronavirus (COVID-19), additional safety and sanitation measures are in effect at 